    "y_cut": 0.44,
    "x_description": "How concentrated power is in the governing coalition (LB + CLB) vis-à-vis the opposition. 1 = OB dominates, 5 = governing coalition dominates. Mean ≈ 3.28.",
    "y_description": "How concentrated power is in the leader's bloc within the governing coalition (LB vs CLB). PCA-weighted index of LB-vs-CLB power ratio, likelihood of CLB defection, LB hierarchy and LB cohesiveness; min-max normalised. Mean ≈ 0.44."
